        "action": "Require restaurants to offer a non-religiously slaughtered meat option",
        "additional_details": "The Government should implement a new law that makes it a legal requirement for food establishments to offer a non-religiously slaughtered meat option for people to choose.",
        "background": "Some food establishments only offer meat that has been religiously slaughtered. I believe this could isolate some of the population who do not eat religiously slaughtered meat.",
